metadata.name: Phosphor.
metadata.description: In the months before the creation of the art, I went through many moments of being hated, loved, a complete confusion that made me have a very difficult ego death, made me realize that things are not so easy but that certainly didn't discourage me, just it gave me more energy to continue and be the best at what I want, completely open to interpretation but my state while I was doing it can open your eyes a little.
